sentences.english: Number two on the list is Karnak temple that is situated neat Luxor, Egypt.
sentences.chinese: 排在第二位的是卡納克神廟，它位於埃及的盧克索。
從一個叫盧克索的地方。

sentences.english: Luxor is about six hundred forty four kilometers south of Cairo.
sentences.chinese: 盧克索約六百四十四公里開羅南部。

sentences.english: Luxor is kinda where you start from.
sentences.chinese: 盧克索是有點當你起步之處。

sentences.english: There has been no violence in Luxor; none of our clients wanted to leave.
sentences.chinese: 在盧克索沒有暴力，我們的顧客也不願退團。

sentences.english: Alongside Nile, opposite the river is Valley Of The Kings, Luxor, Egypt.
sentences.chinese: 尼羅河畔，對岸就是盧克索國王谷，埃及。
